@startuml MCP Agent ReAct时序图
title MCP Agent ReAct模式时序图 - 完整交互流程

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEFECE

actor User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "AgentEngine" as Agent #LightBlue
participant "Conversation" as Conv #LightGreen
participant "ToolOrchestrator" as Tools #LightYellow
participant "OllamaClient" as LLM #Pink
participant "McpClient" as MCP #LightCoral

== 用户输入 ==

User -> CLI: 输入消息
CLI -> Agent: process_message(user_message)
activate Agent

note right of Agent
  **agent_engine.py:66-89**
  process_message() 方法
end note

Agent -> Conv: add_user_message(message)
activate Conv
Conv --> Agent: 消息已添加
deactivate Conv

Agent -> Agent: _process_with_tools(max_iterations=5)

== ReAct循环开始 ==

Agent -> Conv: get_messages_for_llm()
activate Conv
note right of Conv
  返回对话历史:
  - 系统提示
  - 用户消息
  - 之前的助手响应
  - 之前的工具结果
end note
Conv --> Agent: messages[]
deactivate Conv

== Think (思考) ==

Agent -> LLM: chat(messages, temp=0.7)
activate LLM
note right of LLM
  **ollama_client.py**
  调用 Ollama API
  模型: qwen2:0.5b
  endpoint: /api/chat
end note
LLM --> Agent: llm_response
deactivate LLM

Agent -> Tools: parse_tool_calls(response_text)
activate Tools
note right of Tools
  **response_parser.py**
  检测工具调用语法
end note
Tools --> Agent: ParsedResponse
deactivate Tools

== 工具推断 (可选) ==

Agent -> Agent: _infer_tool_calls(user_message)
note right of Agent
  **agent_engine.py:208-276**
  正则表达式匹配 (仅在需要时)
end note

== Act (行动) ==

Agent -> Conv: add_assistant_message(response, tool_calls)
activate Conv
Conv --> Agent: 已添加
deactivate Conv

alt 有工具调用

  loop 每个工具调用
    Agent -> Tools: execute_tool(name, arguments)
    activate Tools

    Tools -> MCP: call_tool(name, arguments)
    activate MCP
    note right of MCP
      **mcp/client.py**
      HTTP POST to MCP Server
      endpoint: /tools/call
    end note
    MCP --> Tools: ToolResult
    deactivate MCP

    Tools --> Agent: result
    deactivate Tools

    Agent -> Tools: format_tool_result(name, result)
    activate Tools
    note right of Tools
      格式: [Tool: name] result
    end note
    Tools --> Agent: formatted_result
    deactivate Tools

    Agent -> Conv: add_tool_message(name, result)
    activate Conv
    Conv --> Agent: 已添加
    deactivate Conv
  end

else 无工具调用

  note right of Agent
    **agent_engine.py:139-155**
    无工具调用，准备返回响应
  end note

  Agent -> Agent: 设置 final_response

  Agent --> CLI: final_response
  deactivate Agent
  CLI -> User: 显示最终响应

end alt

@enduml
